overview:
Prime Realty is based out of Oakland, CA and specializes in REO property listings. With over a decade of experience, Prime Realty is REOtrans certified, Five Star certified, and Res.net certified.

Prime Realty employs 10 personnel for pre-marketing, listing, property preservations, BPO, MSR services and property sales.

Servicing areas such as the Alameda, Contra Costa and Solano counties.

Prime Realty is currently associated with the Oakland Board of Realtors, Multiple Listing Service, and REObrokers.com.

Prime Realty has a eccentric list of Agents that will strive to please our buyers. Not only are the agents here at Prime Realty Honest, and Empathetic, they work extra hard to keep our buyers happy.

If you dont have an Agent, Prime Realty can direct you to one that best suits your needs.

Contact us by email or website www.primerealtyoakland.com
